Definition: a freely moving joint in which movement is limited to rotation
Example: the articulation of the radius and ulna in the arm is a pivot joint
Synonyms: rotary_joint, rotatory_joint, articulatio_trochoidea, synovial_joint, a, freely, moving, joint, in, which, movement, is, limited, to, rotation, the, articulation, of, radius, and, ulna, arm, pivot
Category: noun.body
